name: Alony: Time Travel
description:
EN-US

Alony: Time Travel is a Game where you Travel through Alony's Consciousness!!!

The Game was Made it for Game Jam: https://itch.io/jam/mgdjam6

An Adventure Game following the idea of What Alony's Games in the Future would be like.

I'll have to remake them, but keeping the Appearance, and Idea!!!
